Contemporary Ghanaian brand Chiip O Neal has unveiled its collection for the Spring/Summer 2021 season tagged “Nomadishi – An Evolutionary Wonder”. In a statement following the release, the brand explained that the new collection tells a narrative of the evolution of mankind. Introducing the lookbook that expresses a strong cultural identity and reinforces our connections with each other worldwide. Nomadishi collection is a woven tapestry of all cultures that have different great influences and deep meaning for the essence of life. See the full lookbook below Credits:
